text: Marieve "Maria" Herington (born 22 February 1988) is a Canadian actress, singer, and voice actress. She is best known for voicing Tilly Green from Big City Greens. ==Other websites== * Marieve Herington at Behind The Voice Actors * Category:1988 births Category:American video game actors Category:American voice actors Category:Canadian movie actors Category:Canadian voice actors Category:Living people
